channel.title: Ye Olde Waffle Comic Frames
channel.description:
So after returning here, and seeing that Leak-Free no longer exists, I dug through my old comics and deleted some of the old files that didn't really merit staying there - comics in progress, mostly. However, I saved some of the good ones. They don't have dialog, and I have no idea what is going on in any of them. However, they're somewhat entertaining (to me, at least) so I will be posting all of the good ones I can find in this thread. I liked doing these old comics - I was getting very, very good at posing but I couldn't edit worth a damn, so they weren't very high quality.
The first is a series featuring Jambo, apparantly doing... something in a prison.

This one, which I managed to pull out of the poses for Arctic Antics 12, was part of Jambo's acid trip across America.
